	=== Eclipse RAP Tutorial
			 This tutorial describes how to create
				Eclipse RAP
				applications and how to use the CSS theming to modify their look.
				Eclipse RAP aims to enable developers to build
				rich,
				Ajax-enabled web
				applications by using the Eclipse development
				model. 
			  This tutorial is based on Eclipse 3.7 (Indigo).
			
		
	
